extends ../../layouts/default

block content
  - var action = 'save'

  if (typeof errors !== 'undefined')
    .fade.in.alert.alert-block.alert-error
      a.close(data-dismiss="alert", href="javascript:void(0)") x
      ul
        each error in errors
          li= error.type
  .row.well
    .span5
      if (!essay.isNew && essay.image && essay.image.files && essay.image.files.length)
        img(src=essay.image.cdnUri + '/mini_' + essay.image.files[0])
      h4= essay.description
      h4= essay.context
      h4= essay.reflection
      hr
    .span6
      form(method="post", action=action, enctype="multipart/form-data")
        if (!essay.isNew)
          input(type="hidden", name="_method", value="PUT")
        .control-group
          label.control-label(for='context') Itâ€™s time to weave together the components of your essay. You may need to add, cut, or include transitions. Let the larger idea of the essay guide your decisions. You may begin with description and build suspense, or lead in slowly with context, or make an impact with reflection. However you decide to begin, your first sentence should hook your readers from the get-go.
          p Using the existing writing you've already done, piece together your final essay here:
          .controls
            textarea#org.input-xlarge(type='text', rows="50", name="organization")=essay.organization
        .form-actions
          button.btn.btn-success.pull-right(type='submit') Submit Final Draft
